Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.24,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:18.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:22.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:26.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:30.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:33.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:40.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:48.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:51.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:59.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:11.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:15.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:19.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:40.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the dark corners of this\Npeaceful-looking town
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,lurks the evil organization, Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:49.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is the mission of Hongo Takeshi, the\NKamen Rider, to expose and eliminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:54.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is for this reason that\NGel Shocker considers Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to be their greatest enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:02:02.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,General Black has once again\Nreceived the order to kill Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What cyborg monster will\Nhe choose to send today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:12.57,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(537.167,200.389)}Rider in Peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:12.57,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,700.389)}Isogin Jaguar's Hellish Trap
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,Isogin Jaguar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:19.41,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill Hongo Takeshi, the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,That is the reason we\Nmade you what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:27.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,Killing the Kamen Rider will\Nbring joy to Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:32.67,Italics,,0,0,0,,It will bring joy to me, General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.09,Italics,,0,0,0,,And, Isogin Jaguar...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:37.81,Italics,,0,0,0,,It will bring joy to you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:43.84,Italics,,0,0,0,,Isogin Jaguar... kill the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.31,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:49.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.36,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:18.22,Italics,,0,0,0,,You must kill the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:24.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,You exist to kill the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.22,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.89,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never do something so awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill him! You must kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.79,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:00.81,Italics,,0,0,0,,You are no ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:06.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,You are a cyborg we\Ncreated... Isogin Jaguar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:10.36,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yes. You are Isogin Jaguar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.42,Italics,,0,0,0,,Now you must go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.56,Italics,,0,0,0,,Go forth, and kill Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw me, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days has your\Nfather been missing, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done everything to find him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but we haven't found\Nthe smallest trace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up already, Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki of the Rider\NCorps will be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It took you long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Choco.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You said something was up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. This isn't a date, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.\NThis is no time for jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my friend, Katsuragi Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Her father went missing ten days ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Any idea where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki lived alone with her father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get the entire Kamen\NRider Kid Corps mobilized and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry!\N- Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Send a pigeon back to HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the hubbub, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Choco... Choco's friend\Nwas taken by Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... this is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And right in front of Taki, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, Yokko, Naoki, Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Request aid from the Kamen\NRider Kid Corps at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What should the message be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Find a red-and-yellow rally car."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Find a red-and-yellow rally car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Find a red-and-yellow rally car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Find a red-and-yellow rally car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Find a red-and-yellow rally car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.67,Italics,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker kidnapped a friend of Choco's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.64,Italics,,0,0,0,,Taki is tracking them via helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.62,Italics,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, we're counting on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the red-and-yellow rally car!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You found the red-and-yellow rally car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Chiba-bound along Route 128!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... that's in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool Hongo Takeshi didn't\Nrealize this was a trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That we intentionally used an eye-catching\Ncar that even a child could recognize,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and drove in a way to call attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.73,Italics,,0,0,0,,This isn't good... he's going to lose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:13.52,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Gel Shocker cyborg... Isogin Jaguar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You... return Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isogin Jaguar Feeler Camouflage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste the poison of Isogin Jaguar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isogin Jaguar Killer Feeler Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you impressed by my power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... I was hoping I could find that\Nrally car around here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back! That's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki is here with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... I see Maki is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... and we also found her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it, Taki?\N- That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my father right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I understand now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:37.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,The transformation device is in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.16,Italics,,0,0,0,,If I can just destroy it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Point Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back! He's not your father anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe! Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:25.48,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:26.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.34,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.18,Italics,,0,0,0,,You must kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dad!\N- Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dad!\N- Maki...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:56.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The horrors wrought by Gel Shocker\Nare the same as the horrors wrought by war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:23:01.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They'll happily tear apart\Nfamilies if it serves their ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...\Nkeep fighting! Save them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:08.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keep fighting, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,100,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.60,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:14.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Listen, my Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:17.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let us celebrate the birth of Utsubogames.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:19.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Utsubogames...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:23.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Use your killer smog\Nand steel-cracking shell
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:25.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to destroy Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.06,0:23:27.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen... let us\Nmeet again next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,for "The Sludge Monster's\NTerrifying Killer Smog."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy80\fs113\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(527.167,720.389)}The Sludge Monster's\NTerrifying Killer Smog
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:50.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:57.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:01.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.70,0:24:05.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:09.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.16,0:24:13.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider in Peril!\NIsogin Jaguar's Hellish Trap